data.title: CONTENTdm
data.meta_description:
This is the second part of a two-part recording in which Sacred Harp singers Margie Broxton, Willie, Ethel Roney, Carrie Tidwell, and Eunice F. Stevens sing untitled Sacred Heart songs usually sung during church services or family gatherings. They sing each in solfege before incorporating lyrics. 

The first song is from 00:18-2:00.
The second song is from 2:00-3:57.
The third song is from 4:00-5:30.
The fourth song is from 6:00-6:49.
The fifth song is from 6:57-8:20.
The sixth song is from 8:25-9:27.
The seventh song is from 9:45-10:25.
The eighth song is from 10:43-12:33.
